	cookies | Randstad Czech






 take control of your cookies.At Randstad we combine the power of technology with the passion of our HR professionals to create an experience that’s more human. To achieve this goal we use technology to our advantage, including cookies. Cookies help us to provide a seamless browsing experience by recognizing you each time you visit the site and helping us to understand what parts of the website you find most interesting. The cookie settings on this site are set to ‘allow all’– but if you want, you can change your settings at any time. If you do, you may lose some functionality. More info can be found in our our website uses
